\c 187 
\pc \bd 187\bd*

\s Kama una mahitaji
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Kama una mahitaji, huna mali nyingi tena, Njaa vile ikifika kwako nyingi, Ukumbuke \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  Baba analinda kila saa, Leta taabu yako yote kwake Yesu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uiache yote kwake, Acha taabu yako yote kwake Yesu\bdit*\bdit ;\bdit*\bdit  Ukimusadiki \bdit*\bdit Mungu\bdit*\bdit , atakupatisha nguvu, Acha taabu yako yote kwake.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wewe ni mugonjwa vile, mwili unauma sana, Taabu inaleta woga mwingi kwako\bd*\bd ?\bd*\bd  Yesu anajua yote naye atakusaidia, Leta taabu yako yote kwake Yesu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uiache yote kwake, Acha taabu yako yote kwake Yesu; Ukimusadiki Mungu, atakupatisha nguvu, Acha taabu yako yote kwake.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Kama wewe ni muzee, unachoka sikuzote, Ee, usisahau \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  yuko nawe\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Yesu ni karibu sasa, na atakuchunga sana, Leta taabu yako yote kwake Yesu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uiache yote kwake, Acha taabu yako yote kwake Yesu; Ukimusadiki Mungu, atakupatisha nguvu, Acha taabu yako yote kwake.\bdit*
